line_1: Thou'dst need no more wert thou to take thy Lodging Under-ground.
line_2: Thou sleep'st each Night in so much Sear-cloth bound,

line_2: Invite Repose, and make my Sleep more sound:

line_1: A while it floated 'till born Under-ground,
line_2: 'Twas in th' Abyss of deep Oblivion drown'd.
